  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为餐厅订座系统画一个状态图，核心是桌子的生命周期。桌子一开始应该是\"空闲\"状态，然后可以被预订、占用，或者进入维护。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Livre",
        "Reservada",
        "Ocupada",
        "Indisponivel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我理解为：空闲(Livre)是初始状态，然后分支到预订(Reservada)或直接占用(Ocupada)。那维护状态(Indisponivel)是终态还是可以恢复的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Livre",
        "Reservada",
        "Ocupada",
        "Indisponivel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "维护后可以恢复，要有一条线回到空闲。另外，预订取消、客户到达、客户离开这些场景都要有转换。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Indisponivel",
        "Livre",
        "Reservada",
        "Ocupada"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先搭建主干：从初始节点到空闲，然后空闲可以转到预订或直接占用，占用结束后回到空闲。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[Education_ContentCDN]",
        "Livre",
        "Reservada",
        "Ocupada"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还要考虑紧急情况——占用中的桌子可能因突发事件进入维护，预订中的桌子也可能被后台锁定。另外维护完成后标注\"再次可用\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ocupada",
        "Indisponivel",
        "Reservada",
        "Livre"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下转换标签：空闲→预订是\"预订完成\"，空闲→占用是\"客户无预订入座\"，预订→占用是\"客户到达\"，占用→空闲是\"客户离开\"，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Livre",
        "Reservada",
        "Ocupada"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，预订取消回到空闲，维护的触发条件分三种：空闲时是\"维护\"，预订时是\"锁定\"，占用时是\"紧急\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reservada",
        "Livre",
        "Indisponivel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。标题定为\"状态图 - 桌子状态\"，所有转换和标签已按你要求的场景配置，维护状态可以回到空闲并标注\"再次可用\"。",
